East 143rd Street, south side, west from the Third Avenue Elevated structure (west of Willis Avenue) to Alexander Avenue, showing where the W.P.A. is going to carry out improvement activities.

Five Boroughs Project

Intersection of Third (right) and Alexander Avenues, looking south. The building with the tank on the top is Loew's Scenic Studio. Several four-story buildings formerly occupied the triangular block where the gasoline station is. View 3 shows a closeup of the east side of Third Avenue.
